      <uri>https://www.thunderbird.net</uri>
    </author>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/144.0/releasenotes/"/>
    <updated>2025-10-14T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <published>2025-10-14T00:00:00+00:00</published>

    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      

  
  

  
    

    
      
        
        

        
          <h3>Changed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Flatpak runtime has been updated to Freedesktop SDK 24.08</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Fixed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Copying text from some error alerts was not possible</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Fastmail CalDAV app password access failed due to forced OAuth regression</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Delete key failed to prevent deleting attachments in OpenPGP messages</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Newly created folder was missing under "Recent" when moving a message</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Sender avatar displayed incorrectly for <code>'Name' via address</code> sender format</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Sorting by threads only brought threads with unread top messages to the top</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>News message marked read after NNTP error prevented retrieval from server</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Inbox 'Location' column was not translated in French locale installation</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Not all headers were signed when creating digitally signed OpenPGP email</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Users could not read mail signed with OpenPGP v6 and PQC keys</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Testing a configured personal S/MIME certificate for a sub-identity did not work</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Testing an S/MIME certificate did not work for an old invalid certificate</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Changing identity in compose window caused modified draft not to be saved</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Shift-click 'Compose Message To' on 'mailto' link did not open in plain text</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Image preview in Insert Image dialog failed with CSP error for web resources</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash in various scenarios</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>'Copy Message to' action in a newsgroup filter did not work</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could not import profile located at the top level of zip file</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird did not clearly fail when importing profile from a bad source</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>No way to distinguish between Thunderbird Release/ESR in Windows registry</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Multi-attachment delete/detach confirmation only cited first attachment</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird hung when auto-checking multiple accounts for new messages</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Reply All button was missing when using a Microsoft Exchange account</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Sending emails via servers with self-signed certificate did not work</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Task reminders could fail for tasks without end dates or with shifted due dates</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Could not copy an event in multiweek or month view by drag-and-drop</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Calendar discovery with certificate error displayed multiple exceptions</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual and UX improvements</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/security/known-vulnerabilities/thunderbird/#thunderbird144">Security fixes</a></p>
          
        </li>
      
    
    </ul>
  
  

<p>As always, you’re encouraged to <a href="https://connect.mozilla.org/t5/ideas/idb-p/ideas/label-name/thunderbird">tell us what you think</a>, <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/questions/new/thunderbird">ask for help</a>, or <a href="https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=Thunderbird">file a bug in Bugzilla</a></p>
